<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4122218>
    dc:description "Figs 436–450. Papuan and Wallacean Maechidius Macleay, 1819, legs, various views. 436. M. hirtipes Arrow, 1941, lectotype, ♂, basal metatarsomere (BMNH). 437. M. tarsalis Arrow, 1941, lectotype, ♂, basal metatarsomere (BMNH). 438. M. babyrousa sp. nov., paratype, ♀, metatibial terminal spurs (BMNH). 439. Same, paratype, ♂ (BMNH). 440. Same, different aspect (BMNH). 441. M. yamdena sp. nov., paratype, ♀, metatibial terminal spurs (BMNH). 442. Same, paratype, ♂ (BMNH). 443. M. longipes sp. nov., holotype, ♂, metatibial terminal spurs (BMNH). 444. M. ursus sp. nov., holotype, ♀, left metatibia and basal metatarsomere (NME). 445. M. dani sp. nov., holotype, ♂, apical portion of metatibia (IECA). 446. M. skalei sp. nov., holotype, ♂, apical portion of metatibia and basal metatarsomere (NME). 447. M. yamdena sp. nov., paratype, ♂, protibial terminal spur (BMNH). 448. Same, paratype, ♀ (BMNH). 449. M. babyrousa sp. nov., paratype, ♀, protibial terminal spur (BMNH). 450. Same, paratype, ♂ (BMNH). Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4122218/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4122222>
    dc:description "Figs 451–468. Papuan and Wallacean Maechidius Macleay, 1819, pygidium, dorsal view. 451. M. aenescens Heller, 1910, lectotype, ♀ (SNSD). 452. M. aiyura sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (BMNH). 453. Same, different aspect (BMNH). 454. M. alesbezdeki sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NME). 455. M. angusticeps Arrow, 1941, holotype, ♂ (BMNH). 456. M. aroae Heller, 1914, lectotype, ♀ (SNSD). 457. M. awu sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (IECA). 458. M. babyrousa sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (BMNH). 459. Same, paratype, ♀ (BMNH). 460. M. bintang sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NME). 461. M. boessnecki sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (SNSD). 462. M. brocki sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (BMNH). 463. M. caperatus sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NME). 464. M. ciliatus sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (IECA). 465. M. crypticus sp. nov., paratype, ♂ (BMNH). 466. Same, paratype, ♀ (BMNH). 467. M. dani sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (IECA). 468. M. deltouri sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (BMNH). Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4122222/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4122126>
    dc:description "Figs 8–13. Maechidius divergens (Waterhouse, 1875) comb. nov., ♂ (BMNH). 8. Habitus, dorsal view. 9. Head, dorsal view. 10. Same, ventral view. 11. Head, ventral view and antennal pockets. 12. Prosternum and pronotal hypomera, ventral view. 13. Left protibia. Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4122126/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4122258>
    dc:description "Figs 751–753. Dry nutrient-poor semi-dry slopes in eucalypt stands near Doyo Lama village, Sentani env., North New Guinea. Numerous Maechidius lobaticeps Frey, 1969 and the type series of M. nepenthephilus sp. nov. were sampled from flowers and pitchers of Nepenthes sp. in this area." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4122258/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4122206>
    dc:description "Figs 286–301. Papuan and Wallacean Maechidius Macleay, 1819, elytron, dorsal view. 286. M. aenescens Heller, 1910, lectotype, ♀ (SNSD). 287. M. aiyura sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (BMNH). 288. M. alesbezdeki sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NME). 289. M. angusticeps Arrow, 1941, holotype, ♂ (BMNH). 290. M. aroae Heller, 1914, lectotype, ♀ (SNSD). 291. M. paupianus Heller, 1910, ♂ (BMNH). 292. M. awu sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (IECA). 293. M. babyrousa sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (BMNH). 294. M. bintang sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NME). 295. M. boessnecki sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (SNSD). 296. M. brocki sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (BMNH). 297. M. caperatus sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NME). 298. M. ciliatus sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (IECA). 299. M. crypticus sp. nov., paratype, ♀ (BMNH). 300. M. dani sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (IECA). 301. M. deltouri sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (BMNH). Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4122206/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4122212>
    dc:description "Figs 333–348. Papuan and Wallacean Maechidius Macleay, 1819, elytron, dorsal view. 333. M. pauxillus Heller, 1910 comb. rest., lectotype, ♂ (SNSD). 334. M. pedarioides Arrow, 1941, syntype, ♂ (BMNH). 335. M. peregrinus Lansberge, 1886, ♂ (DTC). 336. M. popei (Frey, 1969) comb. nov., holotype, ♀ (BMNH). 337. M. perlatus (Frey, 1969) comb. nov., ♂ (SMNS). 338. Same, enlarged (SMNS). 339. M. riedeli sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (SMNS). 340. M. rugicollis Moser, 1920, lectotype, ♀ (ZMHB). 341. M. seriegranosus Heller, 1914, lectotype, ♂ (SNSD). 342. M. seriepunctatus Moser, 1920, lectotype, ♂ (ZMHB). 343. M. similis sp. nov., paratype, ♂ (BMNH). 344. M. skalei sp. nov., paratype, ♂ (NME). 345. M. sougb sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NME). 346. M. speciosus (Frey, 1969) comb. nov., ♀(BMNH). 347. M. sturnus Arrow, 1941, holotype, ♂ (BMNH). 348. M. subcostatus Heller, 1895, lectotype, ♂ (SNSD). Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4122212/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4122193>
    dc:description "Figs 226–241. Papuan and Wallacean Maechidius Macleay, 1819, pronotum, dorsal view. 226. M. lineatopunctatus Frey, 1969, holotype, ♂ (NHMB). 227. M. lobaticeps Frey, 1969, ♂ (DTC). 228. M. longipes sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (BMNH). 229. M. luniceps Fairmaire, 1883, ♂ (BMNH). 230. M. mailu sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NHMB). 231. M. maleo sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (IRSN). 232. M. merdeka sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (BMNH). 233. M. milneanus Heller, 1914, lectotype, ♀ (SNSD). 234. M. miklouhomaclayi sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NHMB). 235. M. muticus Arrow, 1941, syntype, ♂ (BMNH). 236. M. nanus Arrow, 1941, syntype, ♂ (BMNH). 237. M. nepenthephilus sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NME). 238. M. opatroides Arrow, 1941 comb. rest., lectotype, ♀ (BMNH). 239. M. owenstanleyi sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (BMNH). 240. M. papuanus Moser, 1926, lectotype, ♀ (ZMHB). 241. M. parallelicollis Moser, 1920, lectotype, ♂ (ZMHB). Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4122193/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4122196>
    dc:description "Figs 242–258. Papuan and Wallacean Maechidius Macleay, 1819, pronotum, dorsal view. 242. M. paupianus Heller, 1910, lectotype, ♀ (SNSD). 243. M. pauxillus Heller, 1910 comb. rest., lectotype, ♂ (SNSD). 244. M. pedarioides Arrow, 1941, syntype, ♂ (BMNH). 245. M. peregrinus Lansberge, 1886, ♂ (DTC). 246. M. perlatus (Frey, 1969) comb. nov., ♂ (SMNS). 247. M. popei (Frey, 1969) comb. nov., holotype, ♀ (BMNH). 248. M. riedeli sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (SMNS). 249. M. rugicollis Moser, 1920, lectotype, ♀ (ZMHB). 250. M. seriegranosus Heller, 1914, lectotype, ♂ (SNSD). 251. M. seriepunctatus Moser, 1920, lectotype, ♂ (ZMHB). 252. M. similis sp. nov., paratype, ♂ (BMNH). 253. M. skalei sp. nov., paratype, ♂ (NME). 254. M. sturnus Arrow, 1941, holotype, ♂ (BMNH). 255. M. sougb sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NME). 256. M. speciosus (Frey, 1969) comb. nov., ♀ (BMNH). 257. M. subcostatus Heller, 1895, lectotype, ♂ (SNSD). 258. M. suwawa sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (BMNH). Not to scale." ;
